WEBVTT

1
01:14:21.920 --> 01:14:24.130 
我等了你10分钟 下不为例
l've been waiting for you 10 minutes. Don't do that again.

2
01:14:24.380 --> 01:14:26.060 
这件衣服使我看起来
This dress makes me look

3
01:14:26.080 --> 01:14:27.820 
像一个沃尔沃思灯罩
like a wulworth lampshade.

4
01:14:27.820 --> 01:14:28.590 
我不穿这个
l'm not wearing this.

5
01:14:28.600 --> 01:14:29.790 
我叫你穿你就穿
You wear it because l tell you to wear it.

6
01:14:29.800 --> 01:14:30.760 
我才不穿呢
l'm not wearing this dress.

7
01:14:30.780 --> 01:14:31.740 
当安迪出庭作证的时候
And when Andy's on the stand,

8
01:14:31.780 --> 01:14:32.620 
我希望你拿件毛衣出来打
l want you be knitting.

9
01:14:32.670 --> 01:14:34.800 
打毛衣 噢 看在上帝的份上
Knitting? For Christ's sake.

10
01:14:34.810 --> 01:14:35.780 
打一件婴儿衣服
-A baby garment.

11
01:14:35.820 --> 01:14:36.790 
我不会打毛衣
l don't know how to knit!

12
01:14:36.800 --> 01:14:37.330 
那就学
Then learn.

13
01:14:37.440 --> 01:14:40.100 
那样没办法得到陪审团的同情
That's no way to win the jury's sympathy.

14
01:14:40.130 --> 01:14:41.430 
哦 你不想听我的意见了
You don't need advice anymore?

15
01:14:41.530 --> 01:14:43.780 
你看这儿 代言人先生
Look at here, Mr. Mouthpiece.

16
01:14:44.180 --> 01:14:47.040 
在我看来我才是哪个
lt seems to me that l am the one

17
01:14:47.100 --> 01:14:48.760 
想出好点子的人
who's coming up with the good ideas.

18
01:14:48.870 --> 01:14:50.900 
我讨厌每个人都告诉我该怎么做
l'm sick of everybody telling me what to do.

